list.abstract: 《Spare》是英国哈里王子的首本自传回忆录，于2023年1月10日发售。 该书被翻译成16种语言，不仅写出了对英国王室的诸多不满，也透露了自己的一些亲身经历，包括在阿富汗服役期间杀过25名塔利班武装人员。书名Spare有备用、备胎的意思，据哈里王子的叙述，威廉王子是“继承人”，而自己是“后备人选”。哈里称，查尔斯国王以及已经过世的女王伊丽莎白二世和王夫菲利普亲王会当面叫他“后备人选”。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a little small. Oh, George has found another bit. Oh, maybe that is a spare shelf. And these would be bits too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确实有点小了。噢，乔治又找到了一块板。说不定那是备用的吧。可是你们看这里还有很多板呢。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a little small. Oh, George has found another bit. Oh, maybe that is a spare shelf. And these would be bits too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确实有点小了。噢，乔治又找到了一块板。说不定那是备用的吧。可是你们看这里还有很多板呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Spare the Europa no thought, Jingim.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别再想那个欧罗巴人了，真金。

yingyinNormal.en: Then one thing led to another. Spare us, Claire.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后就一发不可收拾了，你走吧，克莱尔。

yingyinNormal.en: No problem. Great. Here's my spare key. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没问题。太好了，这是备用钥匙，谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, you're the expert. Don't forget the spare.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你是专家，别忘了备用胎。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're saying everyone walks on eggshells to spare my feelings?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你说每个人如履薄冰就是保护我的情绪吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Done. With time a-to-spare. Oooh, that may be a New World's record.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，时间还剩下很多。这可能是新世界记录。

yingyinNormal.en: We can pitch in. Well, whatever you could spare would certainly be welcome.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们能出点。不管你们能拿出多少我们当然都欢迎。

yingyinNormal.en: If I transmit Khan's location to you now, all that I ask is that you spare them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会把可汗的位置告诉你，只要你赦免他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Oil is gone. Oh dear. Luckily I've got a spare can of oil. Well done, Daddy Pig.
yingyinNormal.zh: 机油用尽。噢，天呐。幸好我还另外带了一桶机油。做得好，猪爸爸。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. You rang? How do you talk down a guy in a bomb vest? And spare me the jokes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有事吗？如何说服穿炸弹背心的神经病，别跟我讲玩笑。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, shit. You talked to him. This is exactly what I was hoping to spare you from.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天，该死的，你还是和他谈过了，这可不是我希望你做的。

yingyinNormal.en: King Neptune, sir? Would you spare Mr. Krabs' life if I went to get your crown back?
yingyinNormal.zh: 海王星国王陛下，如果我去把您的皇冠拿回来，您就能赦免克莱伯先生吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, Mummy Rabbit. Have you got any spare trees? We need trees for our desert island.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，兔妈妈，你有多余的树吗？我们需要给荒岛找树。

yingyinNormal.en: King's Barrow is a working farm. There isn't a spare farmyard half as accessible as here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 金斯巴罗农场在运作，没有更近的闲置农场了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, can't you find me some Duke? There must be one spare. So I can put Edith in her place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您不能给我找个公爵吗？肯定还有剩的，好让伊迪丝知道自己的位置。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a hell of an apology. But if it's any consolation, I was never gonna spare your crew.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真让人感动啊，但是我实话告诉你吧，我根本就没想让他们活着。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, it's hilarious. Now here's an approximation of the spare parts available on the space station.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真好笑，现在，这些是太空站中大概有的备用零件。

yingyinNormal.en: Look at all these coins. I'm sure we could spare a few. Go, then. But do not return looking for more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看我们有这么多钱，肯定能剩下点。那去吧，别再回来找我要了。

word_usage.usage:
spare表示本人“花了时间做某事”，一般不可表示“占用别人”。如：
占用了你这么多时间，我很抱歉。
误 I am very sorry I have spare so much of your time.
正 I am very sorry I have taken so much of your time.
spare oneself的意思是“偷懒，不努力”，常用于否定形式。
